data.description: SELLER TO CONTRIBUTE $5,000 TOWARDS RATE BUY DOWN AND/OR CLOSING COSTS! Why wait for new construction when this newer home is move in ready. This charming 4 bedroom/2 bath has a great layout that is spacious and bright. Open concept with large great room and kitchen combo. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, farm sink and an island which would be great for entertaining. Oversized lot provides options for a pool, relaxing and just having fun. This home is conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, schools, and is only 15 minutes from the beach and would be a great place to call home. Come check it out. NO HOA or CDD!
